content.title: Kubuka i-interface yekufinyeleleka
content.howToUseTooltip:
Ngentansi kunetimfanelo tekumaka tale node letingasetjentiswa kukhetsa imisebenti, njengekuchafata, kugcwalisa umbhalo, njll.

Inani lemfanelo lingaphindvwe ekhasini le-app. Uma uhlangabetana nekuphindzaphindza, sicela ubeke letinye tintfo letikhetsiwe temfanelo kute utfole kwehluka.

Ligama lelibovu likhombisa kutsi linani lemphawu liyaphindzaphindvwa, ligama leliluhlata likhombisa kutsi linani lemfanelo lihlukile ekusesheni kwelikhasi lamanje, futsi ligama lelimnyama likhombisa kutsi kute kucatsanisa lokuphindzaphindziwe.
